Text:
Did you know that Louis DeJoy, Trump's hand-picked head of the USPS, is still in charge? And still sabotaging our postal system?
 
@POTUS has worked to remove DeJoy, but Senate Republicans are blocking any progress.
 
We rely on a strong USPS. It’s past time for DeJoy to go.

My heart goes out to Officer Billy Evans’ family, especially his two beautiful children.

@CapitolPolice have endured so much. But they continue to show up every day to protect not just a building, but the democracy it represents.

Rest In Peace, Officer. https://t.co/MrNzOUdCQi

I would like to personally welcome our new @HouseIntel members:

@RepJasonCrow, @RepJimCooper, @RepBrianFitz, @RepTrentKelly, @RepLahood, and @RepMullin

We have much to do to keep our country safe. Looking forward to our work together.
